Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.17,0:22:19.91,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}差し込む一筋の陽
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.04,0:22:26.40,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}夕立の雨上がりに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.69,0:22:32.90,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}気付く夏の匂い
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.26,0:22:41.58,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}ひしめく光が照らす
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.94,0:22:48.46,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}想いに耳を澄ませば
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.00,0:22:57.89,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}聴こえし友の面影
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.54,0:23:05.91,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}夏夕空　薫り立つ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.13,0:23:12.88,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}鮮やかな過ぎ去りし日々
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.19,0:23:20.17,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}心のまま笑いあった
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.45,0:23:26.10,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}あの夏の思い出よ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.52,0:22:12.24,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}微微泛紅的西邊天空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.17,0:22:19.91,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}射入了一縷陽光
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.04,0:22:26.40,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}雷雨之後的寧靜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.69,0:22:32.90,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}覺察到陣陣夏天的氣息
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.26,0:22:41.58,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}聚集起來的光芒映照大地
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.94,0:22:48.46,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}用雙耳傾聽那往日的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.00,0:22:57.89,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}聆聽到的是舊友的臉龐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.54,0:23:05.91,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}夏天的黃昏散發陣陣清香
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.13,0:23:12.88,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}已經逝去的那些栩栩如生的往昔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.19,0:23:20.17,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}真誠的互相嬉笑著的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.45,0:23:26.10,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}那個夏天的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.06,0:23:51.09,biaoti1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(140,550)}秋之夜宴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.62,0:01:35.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天氣已經很涼爽了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.77,0:01:39.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  山中的紅葉會更絢麗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.04,0:01:42.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過幾天去雙葉大壩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.21,0:01:43.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.84,0:01:47.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就帶點什麼色色的東西去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.50,0:01:49.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  不過為什麼要帶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.65,0:01:52.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目你別聽他胡說  我就帶點心去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.83,0:01:54.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就帶飲料
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.01,0:01:57.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目帶三明治吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.72,0:02:04.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  休息日的便當的話  稍微有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.62,0:02:08.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼呢  試著拜託下塔子阿姨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.97,0:02:10.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你肯定會很高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.97,0:02:15.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也會很高興  塔子阿姨的三明治
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.79,0:02:16.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.54,0:02:23.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.92,0:02:25.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  再見
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.99,0:03:05.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖怪在吃著妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.46,0:03:10.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類的氣味  看到我了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.73,0:03:14.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃了你  吃了你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.86,0:03:21.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.77,0:03:26.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃也沒用  我要吃了你  小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.10,0:03:29.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會去吃了你的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.70,0:03:38.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.69,0:03:40.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來  貴志
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.43,0:03:43.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  怎麼了  臉色很差哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.82,0:03:46.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  沒事…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.67,0:03:51.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好  要焦掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.03,0:04:01.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目回來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.76,0:04:02.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貓咪老師
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.16,0:04:06.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  好香的味道  今晚是炸烏賊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.70,0:04:07.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烏賊怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.97,0:04:10.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貓可不能吃烏賊哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.20,0:04:12.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了我不是貓
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.44,0:04:15.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？  怎麼了夏目  那個痣是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.54,0:04:21.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老…老師
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.02,0:04:27.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  手上中詛咒了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.23,0:04:28.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詛咒？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.03,0:04:31.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還笑得出來  呆子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.75,0:04:32.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.60,0:04:44.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  竟對我的獵物下手簡直是豈有此理
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.36,0:04:46.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還要吃你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.80,0:04:48.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平時的話倒是求之不得
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.30,0:04:52.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憑現在的我  很可能被那傢伙給搶了去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.20,0:04:54.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.04,0:05:01.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法了  召喚別的出來代替我做你的保鏢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.06,0:05:03.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,召喚是指？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.62,0:05:05.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用友人帳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.79,0:05:09.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友人帳  這個也能辦到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.70,0:05:12.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲子很得意地說過
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.22,0:05:20.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這副樣子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.52,0:05:21.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.52,0:05:24.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來披上白布站到陣當中去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.05,0:05:26.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用來代替白衣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.03,0:05:33.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知長相和名字就無法召喚  試試看召喚之前的三篠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.97,0:05:37.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目  放下鏡子和友人帳  滴上血
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.99,0:05:38.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.96,0:05:42.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來是需要一片指甲的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.43,0:05:45.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別覺得可以不用付出代價就能和妖怪打交道哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.75,0:05:51.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.56,0:05:52.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.89,0:05:57.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾之守護  現身吾處
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.33,0:06:00.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汝名  三篠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.70,0:06:14.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目大人  很久不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.66,0:06:17.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次沒把名字還給你  很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.92,0:06:20.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三篠  希望你能幫我個忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.01,0:06:22.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暫時陪我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.92,0:06:24.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,善
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.56,0:06:29.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個…啊  比剛才更為擴散了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.47,0:06:31.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  詛咒的印記
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.10,0:06:33.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.85,0:06:36.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我對詛咒並不熟悉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.84,0:06:38.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另召喚代替我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.99,0:06:39.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.97,0:06:45.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是夏目大人  不能在妖怪前顯出軟弱的內心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.09,0:06:49.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖怪會映照出人類的軟弱和陰暗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.87,0:06:53.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用妖怪來填補自己的寂寞…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.10,0:06:59.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三篠  對主人態度可真差
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.86,0:07:01.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別太得意忘形
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.91,0:07:03.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真說的出口啊  斑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.97,0:07:07.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓印記就這麼附著  真是名不副實的保鏢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.88,0:07:08.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.93,0:07:13.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目大人  對這種不倒翁貓不報指望了的時候  隨時叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.06,0:07:15.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會保護你的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.01,0:07:19.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  誰是不倒翁貓啊  木馬混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.96,0:07:22.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  我去叫丙來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.49,0:07:23.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是不倒翁  醜化優美又可愛的我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.83,0:07:26.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  什麼  是丙？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.05,0:07:28.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認識嗎  老師
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.73,0:07:30.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.57,0:07:44.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲子  玲子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.57,0:07:46.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.63,0:07:48.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於叫我了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.12,0:07:52.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美麗的玲子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.80,0:07:56.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  那蔑視的眼神  冷笑時迷死人的嘴唇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.59,0:07:59.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那頭髮是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.28,0:08:01.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又被人類使壞了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.91,0:08:04.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讓我失望啊  人類
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.63,0:08:08.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碰你的人們就由我丙來作怪殺死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.13,0:08:12.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  沒有胸部
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.80,0:08:17.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  竟…竟然是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.47,0:08:19.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男的！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.14,0:08:23.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙是重度玲子癡迷者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.69,0:08:26.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.50,0:08:28.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且討厭男人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.71,0:08:30.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  這聲音是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.44,0:08:32.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斑嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.60,0:08:33.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.60,0:08:39.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這副臭臉是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.89,0:08:42.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想讓玲子喜歡你都做到了這種地步了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.93,0:08:44.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜下來  丙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.62,0:08:46.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目要掃興了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.67,0:08:51.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  這假冒玲子的到底是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.71,0:08:54.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目玲子的孫子  貴志
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.87,0:08:57.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孫子  玲子怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.98,0:09:00.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久以前過世了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.03,0:09:06.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊  怎會如此短暫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.63,0:09:09.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我討厭人類
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.43,0:09:16.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別靠近我  臭男人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.60,0:09:22.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請用吧  你是為了玲子祖母才哭的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.73,0:09:31.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.02,0:09:34.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三篠大人說是夏目在叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.23,0:09:40.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不由得就興奮了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.38,0:09:41.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.71,0:09:47.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是五日印
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.54,0:09:48.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五日印
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.17,0:09:53.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法移動的妖怪會給走過附近的傢伙附上印記
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.07,0:09:57.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經過五天  印記會把其精氣吸乾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.01,0:10:00.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抑或是誘入主人之處吃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.49,0:10:06.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此重複  印記的主人終有一天會得到讓自己自由的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.32,0:10:15.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪  想不起來是從哪進去的了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.57,0:10:19.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是走了人類無法通行的路
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.31,0:10:21.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裏遇到了印記主人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.57,0:10:26.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀  雖然很麻煩  不過我會幫你調查的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.85,0:10:27.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.24,0:10:35.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下麻煩了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.13,0:10:39.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.40,0:10:41.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是妖怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.04,0:10:57.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個也許不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.82,0:11:01.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  手怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.07,0:11:03.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被樹枝給撓了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.59,0:11:05.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.27,0:11:08.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麼行  化膿的話就麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.32,0:11:11.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的  沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.59,0:11:13.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞧  我很結實的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.62,0:11:16.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  給我看…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.68,0:11:24.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.68,0:11:30.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好  果然擴散了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.35,0:11:39.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得這影子像是瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.63,0:11:41.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗  那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.20,0:11:46.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古怪的東西一點點靠近身邊的鬼怪故事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.53,0:11:48.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會給你打電話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.91,0:11:53.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是瑪麗  現在在大門口
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.31,0:11:56.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過一會  又會打電話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.56,0:11:58.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一接電話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.64,0:12:02.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是瑪麗  現在在正門口
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.27,0:12:14.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟這個痣有什麼關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.54,0:12:23.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.30,0:12:30.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明跟玲子長的一樣  別一臉鬱悶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.28,0:12:31.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.81,0:12:34.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道印記主人的真面目了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.72,0:12:38.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被常年封印的強力邪鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.46,0:12:40.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用印記獵取獵物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.71,0:12:43.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢地積蓄力量
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.77,0:12:46.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像再吃一人封印就會解開了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.09,0:12:49.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再一人  是指我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.72,0:12:56.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  而且正一點點取回力量的邪鬼迫不及待地放出了影子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.86,0:13:02.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,影子吸取你的精氣  行動會越來越快
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.00,0:13:07.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然現在還很緩慢  好不容易找到了你的家而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.55,0:13:12.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  你被那傢伙碰到的話  會死哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.02,0:13:25.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師  好大…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.16,0:13:30.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詛咒的影響使得妖力不穩定
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.42,0:13:34.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  可惡  可惡  可惡…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.24,0:13:34.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.16,0:13:34.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貴志
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.05,0:13:37.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貴志回來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.95,0:13:46.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  真奇怪  好像聽到了聲音的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.24,0:13:50.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把那影子吃掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.91,0:13:53.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有印記的人是碰不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.06,0:13:55.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也沒什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.13,0:13:58.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五日印的效力還有四天
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.21,0:14:01.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃過這期間就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.21,0:14:05.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃掉了就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.12,0:14:07.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有四天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.51,0:14:17.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想讓他們擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.22,0:14:25.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  在一起的話不知道會發生什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.94,0:14:37.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露宿  早上再偷偷回去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.64,0:14:39.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔子阿姨就不會發現
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.94,0:15:00.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  混蛋瑪麗  終於進了家門了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.39,0:15:02.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是不回家比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.66,0:15:05.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸好明天開始是連休了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.71,0:15:11.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目  喜歡上外國人了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.70,0:15:13.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英特耐雄納爾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.25,0:15:20.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔子阿姨嗎  我是貴志
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.90,0:15:23.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天開始的三天  我要住同學家裏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.93,0:15:27.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.30,0:15:33.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  誰家  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.41,0:15:35.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…大家都在等我  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.03,0:15:39.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貴志
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.84,0:15:46.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓塔子阿姨擔心了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.77,0:15:48.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我在的話  麻煩就…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.80,0:15:57.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟玲子不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.61,0:16:01.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡人類
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.61,0:16:03.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小時候覺得很難相處
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.07,0:16:07.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  遇到了溫和的人們懂得了溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.81,0:16:10.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想再逃避了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.04,0:16:15.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想變得溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.97,0:16:19.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是個男人  還這麼天真
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.65,0:16:21.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.14,0:16:22.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.30,0:16:28.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.42,0:16:35.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀  那麼讓僅此一次的式神跟隨並保護你怎樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.91,0:16:36.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,式神
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.30,0:16:39.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驅除影子一族之物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.98,0:16:42.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴你召喚方法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.02,0:16:44.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很苛刻的  要用嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.38,0:16:47.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憑你的體力  是一次定勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.71,0:16:51.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出現大人物還是沒用的小東西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.13,0:16:54.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  丙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.94,0:17:01.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼  明明跟玲子很像  為什麼是男人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.35,0:17:19.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.42,0:17:22.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在正式開始前休息一會吧  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.15,0:17:33.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去抓條魚來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.98,0:17:43.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想回…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.86,0:17:44.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.08,0:18:14.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追過來了嗎  卷軸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.57,0:18:27.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃了你  小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.34,0:18:31.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎能讓你得逞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.38,0:18:36.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.83,0:18:37.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.45,0:18:40.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.99,0:18:49.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來自火之通路  驅除影子之物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.21,0:18:58.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.01,0:19:06.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  好小…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.42,0:19:09.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是你的式神嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.85,0:19:44.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.77,0:19:47.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恢復原樣了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.55,0:19:49.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.75,0:19:51.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的印記也在消失
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.25,0:19:56.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.71,0:19:58.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.87,0:20:02.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看著你  我想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.42,0:20:06.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「想保護重要的東西  不想給人添麻煩」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.14,0:20:09.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全是這種感受
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.32,0:20:14.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能重視自己的傢伙  我最討厭了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.34,0:20:18.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.00,0:20:21.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀  真是漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.24,0:20:27.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,試驗了夏目大人一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.32,0:20:32.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我的名字交付給人類保管  這樣好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.11,0:20:33.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,試驗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.27,0:20:37.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我使青蛙把你引到那傢伙那裏的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.45,0:20:40.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三篠  你…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.63,0:20:42.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是被吃了的話  就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.07,0:20:45.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時友人帳就由我來領取
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.06,0:20:46.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.51,0:20:48.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,判定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.17,0:20:50.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不適合
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.81,0:20:54.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是很有趣  我喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.20,0:20:56.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.78,0:20:59.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暫且把名字交你保管
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.59,0:21:01.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒也不那麼討厭被呼及名字
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.54,0:21:03.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.18,0:21:05.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.25,0:21:07.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是夏目的話  可以召喚我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.53,0:21:13.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目  對人類厭煩了的話  隨時可以來我這
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.00,0:21:22.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貴志
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.10,0:21:26.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.72,0:21:29.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再三叫你把聯絡地址告訴我的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.52,0:21:30.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.29,0:21:33.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我坐那裏去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.86,0:21:34.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.87,0:21:37.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我有多擔心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.55,0:21:40.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去同學家住是沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.37,0:21:42.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是得告訴住址吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.69,0:21:44.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是有萬一的話該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.17,0:21:48.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  一晚上我都很擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.51,0:21:50.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點也沒睡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.77,0:21:50.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.58,0:21:52.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到了我家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.00,0:21:54.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在聽嗎  貴志
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.62,0:21:56.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  我在聽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.51,0:21:59.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到了溫柔熱情的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.43,0:22:01.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我最重要的人們生活的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.87,0:22:02.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個家
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.71,0:23:37.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋天的長夜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.05,0:23:39.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熱鬧的祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.66,0:23:41.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,點綴天空的煙火
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.96,0:23:45.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這鎮上遇到了溫柔的人們
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.78,0:23:47.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了他們
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.56,0:23:50.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做到什麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,

